@startuml
title Cognitively mediated holonic demanufacturing — High-level control pattern (local autonomy + uncertainty gate + human escalation)

' --- layout helpers (reduce overlaps) ---
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam dpi 180
skinparam ranksep 300
skinparam nodesep 500

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor black
}

|Customer|
start
:Provide device batch;

|Holonic Shopfloor|
:Execute step (Intake / Disassembly / Sorting / Shipping);
:Try local resolution (rules, checklists, safe fallbacks);

|Digital Twin + Trace|
:Evaluate uncertainty-risk gate;
if (Uncertainty gate: Uncertainty × Risk > threshold?) then (Yes)
  :Append trace event (uncertainty);
  :Update Twin state (context, hypotheses);

  |Cognitive Mediator|
  :Query Twin + Policies + Episodes;
  :Draft recommendation + justification;
  :Estimate confidence / residual risk;

  |Digital Twin + Trace|
  :Assess mediator output\n(confidence + residual risk);

  if (Enough certainty AND risk manageable?) then (Yes)
    |Cognitive Mediator|
    :Send recommendation + explanation;

    |Human Operator|
    :Receive explanation\n(dashboard / audit trail);

    |Holonic Shopfloor|
    :Apply recommendation\n(or stop/quarantine if needed);

    |Digital Twin + Trace|
    :Append trace event (mediated action);
    :Update Twin state (selected path);

  else (No)
    |Cognitive Mediator|
    :Escalate case package\n(state snapshot + options + risks);

    |Human Operator|
    :Review explanation + evidence;
    :Choose action\n(approve fallback / quarantine / manual intervention);

    |Holonic Shopfloor|
    :Execute human decision;

    |Digital Twin + Trace|
    :Append trace event (human decision);
    :Update Twin state (resolved path);
  endif

else (No)
  :Append trace event (normal);
  :Update Twin state;
endif

|Digital Twin + Trace|
:Commit chosen path\n(merge point);
:Update metrics (WIP, yield, quality, cycle time);

|Cognitive Mediator|
:Store episode outcome\n(including human decision if any);

|Customer|
:Receive overview/certificates (optional);
stop
@enduml